Code preview of the table Country

USE DATABASECOUNTRYHL
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYS.SYSREFERENCES R JOIN SYS.SYSOBJECTS O ON (O.ID = R.CONSTID AND O.TYPE = 'F')
WHERE R.FKEYID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY') AND O.NAME = 'FK_COUNTRY_CONTINENT_CONTINEN')
ALTER TABLE COUNTRY
DROP CONSTRAINT FK_COUNTRY_CONTINENT_CONTINEN
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYSINDEXES
WHERE ID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY')
AND NAME = 'CONTINENTFORCOUNTRY_FK'
AND INDID > 0
AND INDID < 255)
DROP INDEX COUNTRY.CONTINENTFORCOUNTRY_FK
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY
DROP CONSTRAINT PK_COUNTRY
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYSOBJECTS
WHERE ID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY')
AND TYPE = 'U')
DROP TABLE COUNTRY
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: COUNTRY */
/*==============================================================*/
CREATE TABLE COUNTRY (
COU_ID INT IDENTITY,
CON_ID INT NOT NULL,
COU_NAME_EN VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
COU_NAME_BR VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
COU_ISO31661_ALPHA2 CHAR(2) NOT NULL,
COU_ISO31661_ALPHA3 CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
COU_ISO31661_NUMBER INT NOT NULL
)
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY
ADD CONSTRAINT CKC_CON_ID_COUNTRY CHECK (CON_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 7)
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY
ADD CONSTRAINT PK_COUNTRY PRIMARY KEY (COU_ID)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: CONTINENTFORCOUNTRY_FK */
/*==============================================================*/




CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX CONTINENTFORCOUNTRY_FK ON COUNTRY (CON_ID ASC)
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY
ADD CONSTRAINT FK_COUNTRY_CONTINENT_CONTINEN FOREIGN KEY (CON_ID)
REFERENCES CONTINENT (CON_ID)
go

Code preview of the index CONTINENTFORCOUNTRY_FK of the table Country

USE DATABASECOUNTRYHL
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYSINDEXES
WHERE ID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY')
AND NAME = 'CONTINENTFORCOUNTRY_FK'
AND INDID > 0
AND INDID < 255)
DROP INDEX COUNTRY.CONTINENTFORCOUNTRY_FK
go

/*==============================================================*/
